description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 67, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 134, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Leverage for East, Nine Lives for South, and 8 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80672-46984-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [134 Votes, Top 15% Score]
